# Monorepo Standards

- This is a Better-T-Stack monorepo managed by pnpm.
- `apps/web`: Astro frontend (Client/Server islands).
- `apps/api`: Hono backend (Cloudflare Workers).
- `packages/db`: Shared Drizzle schema.

## Dependency Management

- Always use `pnpm add` inside specific app directories.
- If modifying shared types, run `pnpm build` in the root to update the cache.
